1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available.]

2
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:03,020
Episode 37

3
00:00:07,800 --> 00:00:08,320
Ya!

4
00:00:22,680 --> 00:00:23,140
Stop!

5
00:00:26,550 --> 00:00:28,280
I shouldn’t have let him sleep.

6
00:00:28,890 --> 00:00:29,180
Hey,

7
00:00:29,850 --> 00:00:30,910
when can we arrive?

8
00:00:32,090 --> 00:00:32,890
Your Highness,

9
00:00:32,890 --> 00:00:34,050
in one hour, at most.

10
00:00:34,720 --> 00:00:35,350
Good.

11
00:00:38,850 --> 00:00:40,180
You are almost home now.

12
00:00:40,890 --> 00:00:43,350
I bet you must have all sorts of feelings
right now.

13
00:00:43,350 --> 00:00:44,090
What a pity!

14
00:00:44,850 --> 00:00:46,050
The minute you are back,

15
00:00:46,050 --> 00:00:47,850
I’ll put you into the death cell.

16
00:00:48,430 --> 00:00:51,100
Because that’s where

17
00:00:51,390 --> 00:00:52,720
you really belong.

18
00:00:55,430 --> 00:00:56,560
I want to see father.

19
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:58,140
Father?

20
00:00:58,970 --> 00:01:00,230
You are not qualified.

21
00:01:06,220 --> 00:01:07,080
Your Highness.

22
00:01:08,260 --> 00:01:09,680
Her Highness asked us

23
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:10,890
to welcome you here.

24
00:01:10,890 --> 00:01:11,510
Good,

25
00:01:12,300 --> 00:01:13,050
let’s go!

26
00:01:20,510 --> 00:01:21,550
There are too many guards.

27
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:22,550
We won’t be able to save Qishao.

28
00:01:22,550 --> 00:01:24,280
Let’s wait for a better chance.

29
00:01:27,720 --> 00:01:29,250
You don’t have to follow me.

30
00:01:29,640 --> 00:01:30,800
Now that I’ve promised you,

31
00:01:30,800 --> 00:01:32,180
I won’t go to the Southern Regions.

32
00:01:32,180 --> 00:01:33,580
Miss, please forgive me.

33
00:01:33,800 --> 00:01:34,850
I promised master

34
00:01:35,100 --> 00:01:36,180
that I’d keep you safe

35
00:01:36,180 --> 00:01:37,390
as long as I’m alive.

36
00:01:38,090 --> 00:01:39,180
But because of the plague
befalls the Southern Regions,

37
00:01:39,180 --> 00:01:41,509
the people there are suffering right now.

38
00:01:41,930 --> 00:01:42,550
Miss,

39
00:01:43,390 --> 00:01:44,430
my duty

40
00:01:44,890 --> 00:01:45,890
is to protect you.

41
00:01:46,430 --> 00:01:47,259
I don’t care

42
00:01:47,800 --> 00:01:48,930
about other things.

43
00:01:49,220 --> 00:01:50,350
Other things?

44
00:01:50,720 --> 00:01:52,180
Those are all people!

45
00:01:52,550 --> 00:01:53,350
A plague

46
00:01:53,430 --> 00:01:54,009
can take

47
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:55,090
thousands of people’s lives.

48
00:01:55,090 --> 00:01:55,600
How can you…

49
00:01:55,600 --> 00:01:56,200
Watch out!

50
00:01:56,680 --> 00:02:00,010
Help! Help!

51
00:02:00,100 --> 00:02:00,640
Don’t!

52
00:02:01,100 --> 00:02:02,100
Help!

53
00:02:03,430 --> 00:02:04,430
Seems that this man

54
00:02:04,430 --> 00:02:06,030
is infected with the plague.

55
00:02:06,680 --> 00:02:07,550
The plague?

56
00:02:09,550 --> 00:02:10,759
Are you from the Southern Regions?

57
00:02:10,759 --> 00:02:11,350
I…

58
00:02:12,260 --> 00:02:14,350
I haven’t been to the Southern Regions.

59
00:02:14,350 --> 00:02:15,890
I heard a plague broke out
in the Southern Regions

60
00:02:15,890 --> 00:02:17,800
on my way,

61
00:02:18,890 --> 00:02:20,180
so I came back.

62
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:22,180
Unfortunately,

63
00:02:23,050 --> 00:02:24,760
I still got infected.

64
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,260
Since you haven’t been to the Southern Regions,

65
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,720
you couldn’t be infected.

66
00:02:30,550 --> 00:02:31,180
Wait.

67
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,300
I don’t think it’s the plague.

68
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:35,550
It’s not?

69
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:38,390
It’s poison!

70
00:02:55,890 --> 00:02:56,550
This poison

71
00:02:56,640 --> 00:02:57,850
is infectious!

72
00:02:59,180 --> 00:03:00,310
A poisonous plague?

73
00:03:01,640 --> 00:03:02,180
Have you

74
00:03:02,260 --> 00:03:03,100
eaten anything

75
00:03:03,100 --> 00:03:04,640
or touched any medicine recently?

76
00:03:04,640 --> 00:03:05,720
I picked up a bottle

77
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,930
days ago

78
00:03:08,850 --> 00:03:09,930
and I took a sniff,

79
00:03:10,470 --> 00:03:12,330
I felt uncomfortable instantly.

80
00:03:13,300 --> 00:03:16,720
And the symptoms have become severer these days.

81
00:03:18,090 --> 00:03:18,820
His symptoms

82
00:03:19,180 --> 00:03:20,260
are similar to the plague report

83
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:22,260
received by the Imperial Hospital.

84
00:03:24,350 --> 00:03:25,350
Since he fell ill

85
00:03:25,470 --> 00:03:27,070
after he smelled the bottle,

86
00:03:27,260 --> 00:03:28,140
then what’s in the bottle

87
00:03:28,140 --> 00:03:29,200
must be the source.

88
00:03:29,850 --> 00:03:30,980
Where’s the bottle?

89
00:03:31,090 --> 00:03:31,850
I…

90
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,300
I threw it down the hill.

91
00:03:34,430 --> 00:03:35,760
Where did you pick it up?

92
00:03:36,890 --> 00:03:38,890
The border between

93
00:03:38,970 --> 00:03:41,800
the Southern Regions and the capital.

94
00:03:59,090 --> 00:03:59,680
Darn it!

95
00:04:00,850 --> 00:04:02,010
If I’m right,

96
00:04:02,350 --> 00:04:03,480
the plague this time

97
00:04:03,680 --> 00:04:04,800
is not a natural disaster,

98
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,730
but a human plot.

99
00:04:06,850 --> 00:04:07,470
In this case, His Highness

100
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,850
won’t be able to address it.

101
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:10,100
If he fails to control it,

102
00:04:10,100 --> 00:04:11,140
he will be in danger.

103
00:04:11,140 --> 00:04:13,350
And the civilians will end up suffering.

104
00:04:13,350 --> 00:04:14,150
Physician Gu,

105
00:04:14,390 --> 00:04:15,510
the imperial physicians only know medicine

106
00:04:15,510 --> 00:04:16,370
but not poison.

107
00:04:16,390 --> 00:04:17,550
I’m sure I can help.

108
00:04:18,550 --> 00:04:19,050
Okay.

109
00:04:19,640 --> 00:04:20,220
Miss,

110
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,610
I’ll go with you.

111
00:04:30,550 --> 00:04:32,550
I think Prince Qin

112
00:04:32,640 --> 00:04:34,700
has arrived in the Southern Regions.

113
00:04:35,260 --> 00:04:36,260
Your Majesty,

114
00:04:36,640 --> 00:04:37,800
he should be there

115
00:04:37,890 --> 00:04:38,890
by now.

116
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,600
I guess

117
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,430
Prince Qin is working hard

118
00:04:41,430 --> 00:04:42,760
for the people

119
00:04:42,850 --> 00:04:44,780
in the Southern Regions right now.

120
00:04:48,550 --> 00:04:50,680
How concerned he is about our country!

121
00:04:54,970 --> 00:04:57,100
But, Long Feiye,

122
00:04:57,680 --> 00:04:59,140
it won’t take long though,

123
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,430
you’ll have to concern

124
00:05:01,510 --> 00:05:02,850
about yourself.

125
00:05:04,050 --> 00:05:05,550
What a pity!

126
00:05:06,140 --> 00:05:07,300
No one will play Go

127
00:05:07,390 --> 00:05:08,800
with me anymore.

128
00:05:08,890 --> 00:05:11,180
Concubine Qing arrives!

129
00:05:14,890 --> 00:05:16,180
Greetings, Your Majesty!

130
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,090
Rise.

131
00:05:18,550 --> 00:05:20,470
Darling, what brought you here?

132
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:21,930
If I were not here,

133
00:05:22,050 --> 00:05:24,100
Your Majesty would be busy with state affairs

134
00:05:24,100 --> 00:05:26,300
and forget to take your medicine again.

135
00:05:27,010 --> 00:05:28,870
Your Majesty, don’t work too hard

136
00:05:29,050 --> 00:05:31,010
and harm your health.

137
00:05:31,260 --> 00:05:32,720
In that case, I’ll never

138
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,800
forgive myself.

139
00:05:35,220 --> 00:05:36,010
Got it.

140
00:05:37,090 --> 00:05:37,690
Come here.

141
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:07,580
Your Highness.

142
00:06:07,930 --> 00:06:09,220
According to your order,

143
00:06:09,220 --> 00:06:09,800
we’ve set up

144
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:10,390
quarantine areas

145
00:06:10,390 --> 00:06:12,010
in the different places of the Southern Regions.

146
00:06:12,010 --> 00:06:13,430
Civilians who are already infected

147
00:06:13,430 --> 00:06:15,890
have been transferred to accept treatment.

148
00:06:22,350 --> 00:06:23,600
Civilians that we’re not sure

149
00:06:23,600 --> 00:06:25,390
whether they have been infected with the plague

150
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,220
have also been transferred to specific

151
00:06:26,220 --> 00:06:27,280
quarantine areas.

152
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:29,640
Both quarantine areas

153
00:06:29,640 --> 00:06:30,900
and residential areas

154
00:06:31,010 --> 00:06:32,340
have been disinfected.

155
00:06:35,090 --> 00:06:35,890
Relief grains

156
00:06:36,220 --> 00:06:37,220
are also provided

157
00:06:37,260 --> 00:06:38,790
at specific place and time.

158
00:06:41,140 --> 00:06:41,970
Remember.

159
00:06:43,180 --> 00:06:43,850
Make sure

160
00:06:43,930 --> 00:06:45,050
the suspected patients

161
00:06:45,050 --> 00:06:46,010
are separated

162
00:06:46,090 --> 00:06:46,800
in the quarantine areas, too.

163
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:47,350
Yes.

164
00:06:47,930 --> 00:06:48,659
What’s more,

165
00:06:49,680 --> 00:06:51,140
remind civilians in the city

166
00:06:51,140 --> 00:06:52,270
to stay at home more.

167
00:06:52,720 --> 00:06:53,350
If any family member

168
00:06:53,350 --> 00:06:54,280
shows symptoms,

169
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:56,680
report it to the government right away.

170
00:06:56,680 --> 00:06:58,680
Examine carefully at the city gate.

171
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:00,790
Stop any suspected patient

172
00:07:01,140 --> 00:07:02,000
from coming in.

173
00:07:02,300 --> 00:07:02,900
Remember,

174
00:07:03,390 --> 00:07:04,680
at this critical moment,

175
00:07:04,680 --> 00:07:05,600
the government

176
00:07:05,680 --> 00:07:06,350
shall act

177
00:07:06,430 --> 00:07:07,350
more orderly.

178
00:07:07,970 --> 00:07:09,370
Don’t make any mistakes.

179
00:07:09,890 --> 00:07:10,970
So the people will

180
00:07:11,050 --> 00:07:12,220
be confident in the court.

181
00:07:12,220 --> 00:07:12,800
Yes.

182
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,260
Your Highness

183
00:07:14,260 --> 00:07:15,520
is indeed thoughtful!

184
00:07:15,850 --> 00:07:17,650
I’ll go take care of it right now.

185
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:43,830
Any soldier gets infected?

186
00:07:44,390 --> 00:07:46,050
Thank you for your care, Your Highness!

187
00:07:46,050 --> 00:07:47,350
They are all healthy.

188
00:07:48,930 --> 00:07:50,180
I guess King Tianhui asked General Mu

189
00:07:50,180 --> 00:07:51,180
to come with me

190
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:53,180
to find out my relationship

191
00:07:53,180 --> 00:07:54,710
with the Southern Regions.

192
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:56,020
Minister Sun,

193
00:07:56,510 --> 00:07:58,350
remember to keep distance from me.

194
00:07:58,350 --> 00:07:59,350
I got it.

195
00:08:00,640 --> 00:08:01,500
Your Highness,

196
00:08:02,140 --> 00:08:04,260
I think the plague this time

197
00:08:04,430 --> 00:08:05,550
is quite odd.

198
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,220
Odd?

199
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:09,090
Yes.

200
00:08:09,390 --> 00:08:10,320
What do you mean?

201
00:08:10,430 --> 00:08:11,550
Usually when a plague breaks out

202
00:08:11,550 --> 00:08:12,890
on a large scale like this,

203
00:08:12,890 --> 00:08:14,390
it’s mostly triggered by flood,

204
00:08:14,390 --> 00:08:16,220
drought, livestock epidemic,

205
00:08:16,510 --> 00:08:17,720
or abnormal changes

206
00:08:17,850 --> 00:08:19,180
of the weather.

207
00:08:19,550 --> 00:08:20,800
But nothing happens

208
00:08:20,890 --> 00:08:22,820
in the Southern Regions this year.

209
00:08:23,640 --> 00:08:25,850
So the plague came from nowhere.

210
00:08:26,550 --> 00:08:27,610
More importantly,

211
00:08:28,390 --> 00:08:29,640
our therapy

212
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,600
doesn’t work at all.

213
00:08:32,090 --> 00:08:33,260
So you mean

214
00:08:34,350 --> 00:08:35,260
this plague

215
00:08:36,140 --> 00:08:37,510
is a new epidemic?

216
00:08:37,970 --> 00:08:38,970
Highly possible.

217
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,659
Your Highness,

218
00:08:42,350 --> 00:08:43,929
I’ll inform the imperial physicians

219
00:08:43,929 --> 00:08:45,760
and ask them to study it right away.

220
00:08:45,760 --> 00:08:46,550
Hope they can

221
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,100
find the cure soon.

222
00:08:48,640 --> 00:08:49,970
Make it as quickly as possible.

223
00:08:49,970 --> 00:08:51,030
I’ll take my leave.

224
00:09:07,350 --> 00:09:08,390
Still alive?

225
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:11,220
Tell the Imperial Hospital
to send more physicians

226
00:09:11,220 --> 00:09:12,050
to keep him.

227
00:09:12,180 --> 00:09:12,720
Yes.

228
00:09:13,090 --> 00:09:13,800
Besides,

229
00:09:15,260 --> 00:09:16,720
whether he’s cured or not,

230
00:09:17,550 --> 00:09:19,150
make His Majesty stay there.

231
00:09:19,510 --> 00:09:20,140
Yes.

232
00:09:20,430 --> 00:09:22,470
His Highness arrives!

233
00:09:23,550 --> 00:09:24,300
Yizheng.

234
00:09:25,550 --> 00:09:26,680
Greetings, mother.

235
00:09:26,970 --> 00:09:28,180
Let me look at you.

236
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,350
Is everything

237
00:09:30,350 --> 00:09:31,800
going well?

238
00:09:32,430 --> 00:09:33,720
It went well at first.

239
00:09:34,300 --> 00:09:35,350
But that little bastard

240
00:09:35,350 --> 00:09:36,220
Jun Yixie

241
00:09:36,470 --> 00:09:37,260
held me back

242
00:09:37,640 --> 00:09:38,970
and made me suffer a lot.

243
00:09:39,140 --> 00:09:41,350
I knew we shouldn’t have kept

244
00:09:42,390 --> 00:09:43,640
such a bane.

245
00:09:44,010 --> 00:09:45,100
I was going to come back

246
00:09:45,100 --> 00:09:46,760
after I caught Poison Master,

247
00:09:46,970 --> 00:09:48,900
but my identity was exposed early,

248
00:09:49,180 --> 00:09:50,430
and Tianning became such

249
00:09:50,430 --> 00:09:51,760
a crisis-ridden place,

250
00:09:51,760 --> 00:09:53,260
so I had to come back first

251
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:54,640
to make another plan.

252
00:09:54,640 --> 00:09:56,430
As long as you are back safely,

253
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,760
the others don’t matter at all.

254
00:10:00,850 --> 00:10:01,430
Mother,

255
00:10:02,140 --> 00:10:03,140
I caught Jun Yixie

256
00:10:03,220 --> 00:10:04,950
and brought him back this time.

257
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:07,350
He defied me and father’s order,

258
00:10:07,430 --> 00:10:09,100
released Poison Master,

259
00:10:09,680 --> 00:10:11,180
and colluded with our enemy.

260
00:10:11,180 --> 00:10:12,850
It’s all capital crime!

261
00:10:13,260 --> 00:10:14,180
I gotta ask father

262
00:10:14,180 --> 00:10:15,440
to punish him heavily!

263
00:10:15,510 --> 00:10:16,550
No need

264
00:10:16,680 --> 00:10:18,760
to bother your father with such a thing.

265
00:10:18,760 --> 00:10:20,760
You can make decisions by yourself.

266
00:10:26,260 --> 00:10:27,920
Your father is seriously ill,

267
00:10:27,970 --> 00:10:29,850
I’m afraid he’ll die soon.

268
00:10:33,390 --> 00:10:33,970
Mother,

269
00:10:35,220 --> 00:10:36,470
then my throne…

270
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:39,860
Yizheng, don’t worry.

271
00:10:40,090 --> 00:10:42,220
I’ve arranged it for you already.

272
00:10:59,010 --> 00:11:01,720
Guards! Guards!

273
00:11:02,720 --> 00:11:05,890
Guards!

274
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,510
-Stay out of this!
-Guards!

275
00:11:07,510 --> 00:11:08,680
Or, you’ll be killed!

276
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:11,390
I… I want some water!

277
00:11:11,890 --> 00:11:13,180
Guards!

278
00:11:22,220 --> 00:11:23,010
But, mother,

279
00:11:23,850 --> 00:11:24,800
why do you

280
00:11:25,180 --> 00:11:26,440
treat father that way?

281
00:11:31,140 --> 00:11:32,050
You still don’t get it

282
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:33,470
after these many years?

283
00:11:36,470 --> 00:11:38,930
I’ve gained a high position and power,

284
00:11:39,470 --> 00:11:40,510
but your father

285
00:11:40,550 --> 00:11:41,930
never favored me.

286
00:11:45,010 --> 00:11:46,740
I actually don’t care about it.

287
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:49,050
As long as I’m still the Empress,

288
00:11:50,140 --> 00:11:51,800
and he passes the throne to you

289
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:53,470
after he dies,

290
00:11:55,430 --> 00:11:57,140
I can put up with everything.

291
00:11:59,640 --> 00:12:01,390
But being ill so seriously,

292
00:12:01,640 --> 00:12:03,440
he still hasn’t issued his will!

293
00:12:03,470 --> 00:12:05,220
It really pushes my button!

294
00:12:08,760 --> 00:12:09,550
Maybe

295
00:12:10,090 --> 00:12:12,300
he wants to pass the throne to Jun Yixie?

296
00:12:21,180 --> 00:12:22,040
Your Highness,

297
00:12:22,850 --> 00:12:24,300
