00:34:55,469 --> 00:34:58,010
But if I die someday,

721
00:34:58,930 --> 00:35:00,300
I’ll let the whole world

722
00:35:00,430 --> 00:35:01,360
know that you are

723
00:35:01,550 --> 00:35:04,010
unworthy of the Emperor of Beili.

724
00:35:04,390 --> 00:35:05,050
So,

725
00:35:05,350 --> 00:35:07,140
you’d better pray

726
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:08,890
